Name: Rob Moore
Bio:
Rob is a Principal Consultant with Readify and specialises in leading teams towards the delivery of business value using Agile and Lean values and principles and by adopting DevOps and Continuous Delivery practices.

Rob has a proven track record of successfully delivering software projects with a particular focus on accelerated business value delivery, measurement and realisation and he has also been a proponent for and leader towards positive cultural change and gradual continuous improvement across a number of organisations, teams and projects.
